OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775920265
OL,3,CReform UK loses to Green Party in by-
OL,4,Celection at 'flagship' council
OL,6,FReform UK has lost its first electoral
OL,7,Ftest at its "flagship" council in Kent
OL,8,Fto the Green Party in a by-election
OL,9,Ffollowing the jailing of one of its
OL,10,Fcouncillors.
OL,12,FThe Green Party's Rob Yates won the
OL,13,Fseat in Cliftonville, Thanet, with
OL,14,F2,068 votes, making up 39% of the
OL,15,Fvote, ahead of Marc Rattigan for
OL,16,FReform UK with 1,767 votes, making up
OL,17,F33%.
OL,26,@oD@MOUoD@VO]
