CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775920265
OL,3,CReform UK loses to Green Party in by-
OL,4,Celection at 'flagship' council
OL,6,FOf his victory, Mr Yates said: "This
OL,7,Fresult shows that across Kent and
OL,8,Facross the country the Greens are the
OL,9,Fantidote to Reform.
OL,11,F"Twelve years ago Nigel Farage was
OL,12,Fparading down Cliftonville high
OL,13,Fstreet, and now we have turned it
OL,14,Fgreen.
OL,16,F"There is a huge appetite here to live
OL,17,Fwith a politics of hope, empathy and
OL,18,Flocal action, rather than a politics
OL,19,Fof division."
OL,26,@nD@`OUsD@AOUxD@AOU{D@MO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
