PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775920265
OL,3,CReform UK loses to Green Party in by-
OL,4,Celection at 'flagship' council
OL,6,FThe 39-year-old offshore wind farmer,
OL,7,Fa Thanet District Council member,
OL,8,Fvowed to continue being a "community
OL,9,Fpolitician who represents everyone".
OL,11,FReacting to the loss of the by-
OL,12,Felection on Friday, a Reform UK
OL,13,Fspokesman said: "Marc and the team
OL,14,Fhave run an incredible, positive and
OL,15,Fprofessional campaign in the midst of
OL,16,Fchallenging circumstances.
OL,18,F"We'd like to thank voters for their
OL,19,Fsupport. The overriding message from
OL,20,Fthis result is, vote Conservative, get
OL,21,FGreen."
OL,26,@pD@[OUqD@cO]uD@QOUzD@AOU}D@GO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
