PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775920265
OL,3,CReform UK loses to Green Party in by-
OL,4,Celection at 'flagship' council
OL,6,FThe Conservatives' candidate Charlie
OL,7,FLeys came third in the by-election,
OL,8,Fgaining 811 votes, which accounted for
OL,9,F15% of the vote.
OL,11,FThe by-election was triggered after ex-
OL,12,FReform UK councillor Daniel Taylor, of
OL,13,FRamsgate, Kent, was jailed for 12
OL,14,Fmonths in February after admitting
OL,15,Fcontrolling and coercive behaviour
OL,16,Ftowards his wife.
OL,18,FThe 36-year-old was suspended from
OL,19,FReform after his arrest in June last
OL,20,Fyear and expelled after he pleaded
OL,21,Fguilty to the crime in January.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
