PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775920265
OL,3,CReform UK loses to Green Party in by-
OL,4,Celection at 'flagship' council
OL,6,FReform won control of Kent County
OL,7,FCouncil (KCC) in May last year,
OL,8,Fsecuring 57 out of 81 seats, but is
OL,9,Fcurrently down to 47 after removing
OL,10,Fsome of them.
OL,12,FElsewhere Liberal Democrats make up 12
OL,13,Fmembers, newly-established Restore
OL,14,FBritain Kent group make up seven,
OL,15,FConservatives hold six seats, Greens
OL,16,Fnow hold six following Mr Yates's win
OL,17,Fand Labour have two.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
