PN,41506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775920265
OL,3,CReform UK loses to Green Party in by-
OL,4,Celection at 'flagship' council
OL,6,FIn the Cliftonville seat last May,
OL,7,FReform UK won 40% of the vote,
OL,8,Ffollowed by Labour and the
OL,9,FConservatives behind them with 22% and
OL,10,F20% of the vote respectively.
OL,12,FThe Greens had come forth with 12% of
OL,13,Fthe vote.
OL,15,FLeader of the Green group at Kent
OL,16,FCounty Council, Mark Hood, said the
OL,17,Fresult on Friday is "seismic" for Kent
OL,18,Fand it confirms "what we already knew
OL,19,F` the tide has turned for Reform UK".
OL,26,@yD@UOUyD@]O]zD@QOU{D@dO]
