CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775920265
OL,3,CReform UK loses to Green Party in by-
OL,4,Celection at 'flagship' council
OL,6,FOn the campaign trail, Mr Yates was
OL,7,Fbacked by former Green Party leader
OL,8,Fand the party's first MP Caroline
OL,9,FLucas, as well as party leader Zack
OL,10,FPolanski making an appearance on the
OL,11,Feve of the election.
OL,13,FThe party leader is set to return to
OL,14,FKent for a victory rally on Margate
OL,15,Fbeach on Friday evening.
OL,17,FMr Polanski said: "This is a stunning
OL,18,Fvictory for the Greens, going from
OL,19,Ffourth place in a year to first place,
OL,20,Fbeating Farage in an area that has
OL,21,Fbeen his heartlands.
OL,26,@yD@SOU
