CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775920265
OL,3,CReform UK loses to Green Party in by-
OL,4,Celection at 'flagship' council
OL,6,F"Reform and Labour took this by-
OL,7,Felection very seriously, sending
OL,8,Fsenior people to campaign in the last
OL,9,Fweek, but the Greens won and Labour
OL,10,Fagain tanked.
OL,12,F"This shows once again, the Greens are
OL,13,Fnow the only challenger to Reform."
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
